OL,3,CCare home temporarily shuts to new
OL,4,Cresidents after critical report
OL,6,FA care home in Jersey will temporarily
OL,7,Fstop taking in new residents following
OL,8,Ffailings found in an inspection.
OL,10,FL'Hermitage Care Home in St Peter has
OL,11,F11 areas which need improvement,
OL,12,Faccording to The Jersey Care
OL,13,FCommission (JCC).
OL,15,FThe regulator's two main concerns are
OL,16,Fthat staffing levels fell below
OL,17,Fminimum requirements and a management
OL,18,Fstyle that negatively impacted the
OL,19,Fhome's culture.
