OL,3,CCare home temporarily shuts to new
OL,4,Cresidents after critical report
OL,6,FInspectors visited the care home on
OL,7,FWednesday 28 and Thursday 29 February
OL,8,Fto gather feedback from residents and
OL,9,Fstaff.
OL,11,FA follow-up review then took place on
OL,12,FThursday 7 March and Monday 18 March
OL,13,Fwhere the officers reviewed care
OL,14,Fplans, staff recruitment, training and
OL,15,Fwellbeing.
OL,17,FBreaking down the 11 points of
OL,18,Fimprovement, two were described as
OL,19,F"areas of particular concern" and four
OL,20,Fto be completed with "immediate
OL,21,Feffect".
