OL,3,CCare home temporarily shuts to new
OL,4,Cresidents after critical report
OL,6,FStaff training regarding competency
OL,7,Fwith medication was said to be
OL,8,F"overdue and not up to date".
OL,10,FThe Commission reported on the home's
OL,11,Fmanagement style and stated: "Staff
OL,12,Fconfirmed hesitancy in voicing
OL,13,Fconcerns or expressing opinions freely.
OL,15,F"Staff gave examples of private
OL,16,Fdiscussions happening in the corridor
OL,17,Finstead of a private space. Staff
OL,18,Fspoke of rudeness, lack of respect and
OL,19,Fa high staff turnover since the
OL,20,Fbeginning of 2023."
