OL,3,CCare home temporarily shuts to new
OL,4,Cresidents after critical report
OL,6,FHealth professionals also raised
OL,7,Fissues with poor communication and
OL,8,Frudeness, one said: "When I tried to
OL,9,Fraise a concern with staff, we were
OL,10,Fignored."
OL,12,FA care resident's relative explained:
OL,13,F"I was not aware of how to raise a
OL,14,Fconcern and hadn't received
OL,15,Finformation concerning this on
OL,16,Fadmission. Communication was poor but
OL,17,Fhas now improved."
OL,19,FHowever, feedback from another
OL,20,Frelative detailed the home as "first
OL,21,Fclass, I am always kept informed."
