OL,3,CCare home temporarily shuts to new
OL,4,Cresidents after critical report
OL,6,FIn response to the report, a
OL,7,Fspokesperson for L'Hermitage Care Home
OL,8,Fsaid: "The health and well-being of
OL,9,Four residents is our utmost priority
OL,10,Fand we take feedback from the JCC
OL,11,Fextremely seriously.
OL,13,F"While the Commission acknowledged our
OL,14,Fdedicated and caring staff team, we
OL,15,Fregret that some of our procedures and
OL,16,Fpolicies did not meet the high
OL,17,Fstandards we set for ourselves.
OL,19,F"We sincerely apologise to our
OL,20,Fresidents and their loved ones for any
OL,21,Fshortcomings.
