OL,3,CCare home temporarily shuts to new
OL,4,Cresidents after critical report
OL,6,F"We have addressed specific concerns
OL,7,Fregarding our agency colleagues -
OL,8,Fwhile all were checked by the
OL,9,Fprovider, we did not appreciate that
OL,10,Fthe JCC required us to retain copies
OL,11,Fof their DBS certificates for
OL,12,Fverification.
OL,14,F"This oversight has now been
OL,15,Frectified. Furthermore, while our
OL,16,Fcolleagues completed medication
OL,17,Ftraining via Boots online training, we
OL,18,Fnow understand that care staff must
OL,19,Falso provide additional evidence of
OL,20,Fcompetence in the form of additional
OL,21,Fqualifications.
