OL,6,F"We have taken steps to ensure
OL,7,Fcompliance with this requirement. All
OL,8,Four nurses are also qualified to
OL,9,Fadminister medications within
OL,10,FL'Hermitage."
OL,12,FThe home has also recruited two new
OL,13,FCommunity Care Managers.
OL,15,FThe full JCC report can be read here.
